\frac{\left|1 - \mathsf{e}^{2 \cdot \pi \cdot \mathsf{i} \cdot \left(\left(2^{t} \cdot \delta\right) - l\right)}\right|}{2^{t} \cdot 2 \cdot \sin{\left(\pi \cdot \left|\delta - \frac{l}{2^{t}}\right|\right)}} \leq \frac{2}{2^{t} \cdot 2 \cdot \left(2 \cdot \left|\delta - \frac{l}{2^{t}}\right|\right)}